    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Mechanically, it operates with the precision expected of a meticulously maintained, low-mileage asset. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of excellence, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine example of the marque.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
